The evidence with the title 'CEO to worker pay ratios: average ceo earns 204 times median ... ' says Aug 25, 2015  ... CEOs were those listed as of 2014 or 2013, whichever was the most recent year available from SEC filings. Median worker total compensation is from Glassdoor salary reports for US workers from 1/1/2009 through 8/17/2015. Only companies with 30 or more Glassdoor salary reports are included. 
